<rows>          - number of rows
<cols>          - number of cols
<y1>            - y1 value of the speckle
<y2>            - y2 value of the speckle
<x1>            - x1 value of the speckle
<x2>            - x2 value of the speckle
<lamda>         - lambda (0,1)
<no. of iter>   - number of iterations